=== 最近事件 ===
[[File:Or_Sasson_-_Rio_2016.jpg|thumb]]
2004年奥运会上，伊朗柔道运动员{{link-en|Arash Miresmaeili|Arash Miresmaeili}}可能因为伊朗政府避免本国选手与以色列选手直接较量的干预措施而在对阵以色列选手{{link-en|Ehud Vaks|Ehud Vaks}}的比赛中未有出赛。官方宣称Miresmaeili因超重而丧失比赛资格，但他后来却获得伊朗政府的12.5万美元奖金，与奥运金牌得主奖金数额相当。[[国际柔道联盟|国际柔道联盟]]曾启动对于Miresmaeili是否故意增重以弃赛的调查；尽管调查结果表明他并非故意弃赛，但他所接受的奖金却引发了猜测。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/3562808.stm|title=BBC NEWS - Europe - Mystery over Iran judo 'protest'|work=bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2016-12-23|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211100/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/3562808.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年奥运开幕前，[[2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会黎巴嫩代表团|黎巴嫩代表团]]拒绝与以色列代表团乘坐同一辆通往[[马拉卡纳体育场|马拉卡纳体育场]]的大巴。黎巴嫩代表团的负责人Salim al-Haj Nicolas承认其曾用身体挡住车门以阻止以色列运动员进入大巴。以色列帆船运动员{{link-en|Udi Gal|Udi Gal}}称，为避免“外交以及肢体上的冲突”，以色列代表团最终乘坐另一辆大巴，之后他补充道：“他们怎么能让这样的事在奥运前夕发生？这样做难道不与奥林匹克所代表的正好相反吗？”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/olympics/36998989|title=Rio 2016 Olympics: Lebanese athletes refuse to travel with Israel team|publisher=[[BBC体育|BBC Sports]]|date=2016-08-06|accessdate=2016-08-07|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809085457/http://www.bbc.com/sport/olympics/36998989|dead-url=no}}</ref>

据以色列媒体披露，沙特阿拉伯柔道运动员{{link-en|Joud Fahmy|Joud Fahmy}}为避免和以色列运动员{{link-en|Gili Cohen|Gili Cohen}}对战，放弃了第一场比赛<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/saudi-judoka-forfeits-rio-match-apparently-to-avoid-israeli/|title=Saudi judoka forfeits Rio match, apparently to avoid Israeli|newspaper=Times of Israel|date=2016-08-07|accessdate=2016-08-15|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815195416/http://www.timesofisrael.com/saudi-judoka-forfeits-rio-match-apparently-to-avoid-israeli|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Fahmy本人、[[阿拉伯卫星电视台|阿拉伯卫星电视台]]以及沙特阿拉伯代表团对此都解释称其是因伤退赛<ref>{{cite news|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/media/print/2016/08/08/Israeli-media-ignore-Saudi-Judoka-s-injury-insist-withdrawal-for-political-reasons.html|title=Israeli media ignores Saudi Judoka's injury, insist withdrawal is political|publisher=Al Arabiya|date=2016-08-08|accessdate=2016-08-09|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811061659/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/media/print/2016/08/08/Israeli-media-ignore-Saudi-Judoka-s-injury-insist-withdrawal-for-political-reasons.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而其他媒体报道称她并没有受伤<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3729101/Saudi-judo-competitor-forfeits-round-match-avoid-going-against-Israeli.html|title=Saudi judo competitor 'forfeits her first round match to avoid going up against an Israeli'|first=Julian|last=Robinson|newspaper=[[每日邮报|Daily Mail]]|date=2016-08-08|accessdate=2016-08-15|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809171112/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3729101/Saudi-judo-competitor-forfeits-round-match-avoid-going-against-Israeli.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

以色列运动员{{link-en|Or Sasson|Or Sasson}}在男子100公斤以上级第一轮比赛中战胜埃及选手{{link-en|Islam El Shehaby|Islam El Shehaby}}，赛后Sasson欲与El Shehaby握手，但被对方拒绝。事后，El Shehaby被国际奥委会以及埃及奥委会遣送回国<ref>{{cite news|last1=Grohmann|first1=Carlos|title=Egyptian judoka sent home over handshake refusal with Israeli|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-rio-judo-egypt-israel-idUSKCN10Q1WC|accessdate=2016-08-16|agency=Reuters|date=2016-08-15|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815220845/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-rio-judo-egypt-israel-idUSKCN10Q1WC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

